    <h1>Privacy Policy for Piggy Scheduler</h1>
    <p>Last updated: May 25, 2026</p>

    <h2>1. Overview</h2>
    <p>Piggy Scheduler ("the App") is a personal tool that automates posting artwork to social media platforms
  including TikTok. This privacy policy explains how the App handles your information.</p>

    <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>The App may access and use the following information through TikTok's API:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Basic profile information (username, display name)</li>
      <li>The ability to upload and publish video/image content on your behalf</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>Your information is used solely to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Authenticate your TikTok account</li>
      <li>Upload and publish content you have chosen to post</li>
      <li>Display your account status within the App</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Data Storage</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Authentication tokens are stored locally on your device only</li>
      <li>No personal data is transmitted to or stored on any third-party server operated by this App</li>
      <li>No data is sold, shared, or disclosed to any third party</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>This App integrates with the TikTok API. Your use of TikTok is governed by TikTok's own Privacy Policy and
  Terms of Service.</p>

    <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
    <p>Authentication tokens are stored only as long as needed. You can revoke access at any time through your
  TikTok account settings under "Manage app permissions."</p>

    <h2>7. Contact</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about this policy, contact: yonghuidesign@gmail.com</p>

